HEADWORD: Courtepy
<hw>Cour"te*py</hw> <pr>(k??r"t?-p?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.  <ets>kort</ets> short + <ets>pije</ets> a coarse cloth.]</ety> <def>A short coat of coarse cloth.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Full threadbare was his overeste <qex>courtepy</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

